Movie App "CINEMA"
This is a simple movie app built with Angular 15 that displays a list of movies with their details. The app has a home page that displays all the movies, a search feature to filter the list of movies, and a details page that displays more information about a selected movie.

Installation
Clone the repository: git clone https://github.com/dinuly23/webdev2.git
Navigate to the project directory: cd movie-app
Install the dependencies: npm install
Usage
Start the server: ng serve
Navigate to http://localhost:4200/
Features
Home Page
The home page displays a list of movies with their images, names, and descriptions. Users can click on a movie to view more details.

Search
Users can search for a specific movie by typing in the search bar at the top of the home page. The list of movies will dynamically update to show only the movies that match the search query.

Movie Details Page
The movie details page displays more information about a selected movie, including the movie's name, description, genres, rating, length, and an image. In addition, the details page shows other movies that have the same genres as the selected movie.

